vate key sign個message令你信個message係legit"},{"pid":"1ba1f4c9997dad1585ba80e3c22d3c3948a929d2","tid":1408804,"uid":28257,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T18:39:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OKqshnR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOKqshnR.jpg&h=816acab7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e21fee60e4aaefc166f34830a7445f986cd9c5c7","tid":1408804,"uid":28257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T18:40:54.000Z","msg":"最簡單，就咁帶一塊大塊D的白板同DRY ERASE MARKER 就可以做現場的通訊"},{"pid":"acfcc92f95ca5f43463655ef36e324a87739a785","tid":1408804,"uid":52271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T18:41:51.000Z","msg":"諗起上次流料事件"},{"pid":"5c3f5fb87ca6bba04d9e4182efce8a76fec24d50","tid":1408804,"uid":277290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"37f781c92f890548fb2df9acdb36a54dd930f77e","tid":1408804,"uid":258258,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T18:25:24.000Z","msg":"真。加密對戰事好重要<br />\n好可惜唔係個個有底<br />\n即使而家開始簡一小撮人訓練亦有鬼呢個問題"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T18:42:27.000Z","msg":"其實唔使訓練；只係計加/解密9成9既messaging app (whatsapp, telegram, signal, etc) 已經做左。真正既問題係無讀心術你點知其他人信唔信得過"},{"pid":"65d76137f93b8dfc464fad593edf611916517a5b","tid":1408804,"uid":247340,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T18:44:03.000Z","msg":"無可能行得通<br />\n只要比其中一隻鬼知解碼方法<br />\n如同虛設"},{"pid":"2246430aa8093b9094a29396a1acfe4064000b8f","tid":1408804,"uid":75765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T18:44:29.000Z","msg":"有組織先可以內部玩sigma"},{"pid":"e85b2b352d9f2d1a6620c02fa04ec5a5e9a6b588","tid":1408804,"uid":260963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1ba1f4c9997dad1585ba80e3c22d3c3948a929d2","tid":1408804,"uid":28257,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T18:39:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OKqshnR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail